{"title":"java生成txt文件乱码","date":"2019-01-30T18:36:51.000Z","link":"post/308","categories":["Java"],"updated":"2019-04-27T12:13:07.008Z","content":"<p>设置编码为<code>Unicode</code>。网上好多方法说设置<code>UTF-8</code>，但是打开还是乱码。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"keyword\">public</span> <span class=\"keyword\">static</span> <span class=\"keyword\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">main</span><span class=\"params\">(String[] args)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\tString encoding=<span class=\"string\">\"Unicode\"</span>; <span class=\"comment\">//字符编码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">try</span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tFile readFile=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> File(<span class=\"string\">\"studentInfo.txt.txt\"</span>),</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\t\twriteFile=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> File(<span class=\"string\">\"studentName.txt\"</span>);<span class=\"comment\">//studentInfo.txt.txt初始编码为Unicode</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//if(readFile.isFile()&amp;&amp;readFile.exists())  </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//&#123;       </span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//读取txt文件时的txt的原始编码格式</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tInputStreamReader inOne = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> InputStreamReader(<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> FileInputStream(readFile),encoding);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tBufferedReader inTwo=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> BufferedReader(inOne);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//BufferedReader inTwo=new BufferedReader(new InputStreamReader(new FileInputStream(readFile),encoding));</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//FileWriter tofile=new FileWriter(\"studentName.txt\");</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tOutputStreamWriter tofile = <span class=\"keyword\">new</span> OutputStreamWriter(<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> FileOutputStream(writeFile),<span class=\"string\">\"gbk\"</span>);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t BufferedWriter out=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> BufferedWriter(tofile);          </span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//BufferedWriter out =new BufferedWriter(new OutputStreamWriter(new FileOutputStream(writeFile),encoding));</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tString s;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">int</span> i=<span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">while</span>((s=inTwo.readLine())!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\ti++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\tout.write(<span class=\"string\">\"(\"</span>+i+<span class=\"string\">\")\"</span>+<span class=\"string\">\"\"</span>+s);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\tout.newLine();</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tout.flush();</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tout.close();</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tinTwo.close();</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//tofile.close();</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\tinTwo=<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> BufferedReader(<span class=\"keyword\">new</span> FileReader(<span class=\"string\">\"studentName.txt\"</span>));</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">while</span>((s=inTwo.readLine())!=<span class=\"keyword\">null</span>)</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t\tSystem.out.println(s);</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"comment\">//&#125;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t<span class=\"keyword\">catch</span>(IOException e)&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t\t e.printStackTrace();\t\t</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t\t&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">\t&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>","prev":{"title":"int数组转化成List","link":"post/309"},"next":{"title":"properties文件的属性值需要换行","link":"post/307"},"plink":"https://1056438464.github.io/post/308/"}